text: Mikhaylovka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Fyodorovsky Selsoviet of Yenotayevsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 286 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yenotayevsky District
title: Mikhaylovka, Yenotayevsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
